r />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/grreiT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/grreiT</a><br />\n//喺上一次人事地震前<br />\n我寫左封投訴信去<br />\n之後客戶服務部係打番俾我<br />\n話幫我終止合約<br />\n餘下一年幾嘅合約都唔使交錢<br />\n我係上網加電視服務一齊cut<br />\n而且連父母屋企都cut埋<br />\n全部都係即cut<br />\n俾個email大家參考<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有線電視客戶服務部:<br />\n<br />\n貴公司粗暴委任資歷欠佳的人士出任新聞總監，不但不會提升新聞部實力，更會嚴重打擊員工士氣，削弱新聞台公信力。本人已終止信用卡自動轉帳，不日歸還解碼器。直至 貴公司委任合適人選出任新聞總監為止。<br />\n<br />\n本人出此下策，是出於對有線新聞的珍惜，希望可以盡一切努力保住一眾新聞部員工及前員工所建立的基業。<br />\n<br />\n希望 貴公司回頭是岸。<br />\n<br />\n投訴人//"},{"pid":"546b4974e8eb5c2f188253244020c5d7544f6c75","tid":2307670,"uid":372131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6cd43b815a5b6386bbdefa50b0ca8a07cd62e8","tid":2307670,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9380188d43732bd6636a8a4fd861e226fa9c949","tid":2307670,"uid":334806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:39:32.000Z","msg":"有線冇英超睇<br />\n都咁多人有裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"為左支持中國新聞組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎封城果陣都仲有記者肯入去採訪"},{"pid":"68fb7400a65b37314fd0a0e56e3c7339badfe588","tid":2307670,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"546b4974e8eb5c2f188253244020c5d7544f6c75","tid":2307670,"uid":372131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"cut左有綫未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgm